"What we need to clarify is that this a very busy production line, six reports last week, the numbers are dizzying," Malunga explained. "What needs to be clarified is that in the tenure of Madonsela, and I was there doing the same thing...the law was not clarified in terms of what happens when something like this happens." "The President has the prerogative to include him, there is no criminal finding against Jordan and he is challenging this which is within how the system works."